task.summary: Fixed RA compute bug in WhatsUpNow.

Added blue color and darker background to theme. Removed CardViews on all layouts. Increased text size on most layouts. Redesigned Solar and Lunar eclipse data and Lunar Occultation data landscape layouts.
Changed the linked text color in the About activity.
Fixed bug in SolarEclipse, LunarEclipse, and LunarOcculation activities where eclipses were not computed after a date selection.
Rewrote the Settings activity. Changed PositionFormat to read from the main SharedPreferences file.
Rewrote LocationTask fragment. Moved the location code into LocationTask. Moved the permission code into LocationHelper and PermissionUtil.
Fixed bug where LocationDialog in visible during permission check after config change. Fixed bug in LocationHelper where the target fragment was null after config change.
Changes based on code inspection. Optimized layouts. Added backup exclusion file.
Updated the version code to 25. Set minifyEnabled to true for the release version.
